data.description: Very nice 3 bedroom split-plan home in quiet Cardinal Pointe.  Located near parks, walking trails and shopping, you will love this well-kept home.  HVAC, dishwasher, refrigerator and garbage disposal all replaced within last twelve months.  Roof is about two years old.  Must see photos to appreciate!
